{
  "id": "bioaccumulation_potential_screening@1",
  "version": "1.0",
  "env_id": "cameo_chemicals_env@0.1",
  "description": "Perform an environmental risk screening for five hazardous chemicals using CAMEO Chemicals (https://cameochemicals.noaa.gov/). Determine the Bioaccumulation Potential for each chemical based on its Octanol/Water Partition Coefficient (Log Kow). \n\nChemicals to screen:\n1. Chlordane (CAS: 57-74-9)\n2. Benzene (CAS: 71-43-2)\n3. Pentachlorophenol (CAS: 87-86-5)\n4. Ethyl Acetate (CAS: 141-78-6)\n5. Polychlorinated Biphenyls (CAS: 1336-36-3)\n\nClassify the risk as HIGH Potential if Log Kow >= 4.0 and LOW Potential if Log Kow < 4.0. Save a report to '/home/ga/Documents/bioaccumulation_screening.txt' listing each chemical, its Log Kow value, and the classification (High/Low) in the following format:\n\nChemical: [Name]\nLog Kow: [Value]\nRisk: [High/Low]",
  "difficulty": "medium",
  "tags": [
    "cameo",
    "environmental",
    "bioaccumulation",
    "log-kow",
    "risk-assessment"
  ],
  "init": {
    "timeout_sec": 420,
    "max_steps": 60,
    "reward_type": "sparse"
  },
  "hooks": {
    "pre_task": "/workspace/tasks/bioaccumulation_potential_screening/setup_task.sh",
    "post_task": "/workspace/tasks/bioaccumulation_potential_screening/export_result.sh"
  },
  "metadata": {
    "output_file": "/home/ga/Documents/bioaccumulation_screening.txt",
    "chemicals": [
      {
        "name": "Chlordane",
        "variants": [
          "Chlordane",
          "57-74-9"
        ],
        "expected_log_kow": 5.54,
        "expected_risk": "High"
      },
      {
        "name": "Benzene",
        "variants": [
          "Benzene",
          "71-43-2"
        ],
        "expected_log_kow": 2.13,
        "expected_risk": "Low"
      },
      {
        "name": "Pentachlorophenol",
        "variants": [
          "Pentachlorophenol",
          "87-86-5"
        ],
        "expected_log_kow": 5.12,
        "expected_risk": "High"
      },
      {
        "name": "Ethyl Acetate",
        "variants": [
          "Ethyl Acetate",
          "141-78-6"
        ],
        "expected_log_kow": 0.73,
        "expected_risk": "Low"
      },
      {
        "name": "Polychlorinated Biphenyls",
        "variants": [
          "Polychlorinated Biphenyls",
          "PCBs",
          "1336-36-3"
        ],
        "expected_log_kow": 6.0,
        "range_min": 4.0,
        "range_max": 8.5,
        "expected_risk": "High"
      }
    ],
    "tolerance": 0.5
  },
  "success": {
    "mode": "program",
    "spec": {
      "program": "verifier.py::verify_bioaccumulation_screening"
    }
  }
}
